channel.title: [317] Fantasy World ~ Zeta
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img192.imageshack.us/img192/8629/testjx.jpg[/img] [/center]
Details: [code=java] Starting base: Delta Current Base: a mix of delta pi & hyperion like Imsuperman05 calls it Coders: RandQm & Imsuperman05 [/code]
[size=12pt][b]The project:[/b][/size] [size=8pt][i]From start to now[/i][/size]
[b]I started this project without the intention to ever do something with this and just to learn the art of coding. I posted 2 development treads just to show off and get feedback how I was going it, I got pretty positive commands what made me proceed this project. Once I was to the point that I posted Fantasy World Alpha, I gained so much positive feedback that I officially decided to proceed and actually finish this project. Due my pure noobisch coding skills in the beginning, what's still pretty poor but is getting descent the whole source is a fail. Then Imsuperman05 came who wanted to help me. He packaged everything and is doing so much for the server that I never would be able to. Actually the plan was to go in Beta already the time I'm writing this, but due the work from Imsuperman05 and more ideas I wanted to put it went slower than expected. But since we proceeded a lot since Alpha I decided to change to zeta. The next week(s) will be adding a few more ideas, shops and drops, improving some things ect, but soon I will officially go into Beta to later host the server. Wish us luck (:[/b]
[ul][size=14pt][b]- Server information:[/b][/size] [list][li]packaging from Imsuperman05[/li] [li]Good economy: barely anything is for sale in shops, all comes from skills! Like rune armour, rune arrows, dragon. All those things have to be gained with skills or quests, whats actually also a skill[/li] [li]Lots of original ideas[/li] [li]rs npcs spread over all the used areas[/li] [li]also animals like sheeps and cows spread over the map[/li] [li]mining guild requires 60 mining[/li] [li]draining run energy[/li] [li]all shops support 1st and 2nd click[/li]
[li]Custom skill (quest skill)[/li] [li]Very descent donator futures: member skills, member island, member monster area ect...[/li] [li]npc drops made for economy: dragon legs, chains, weapons all sorts of stuff gained by kbd & slayer for f2p members, p2p members have more choice with the monster area.[/li] [li]Shops are like real runescape in all active citys, even arhein who sells pineapple in catherby! :D[/li] [li]use of many areas: dagonoth island, canifis, port phasmatys, varrock, edgville, lumbridge, al kahrid, S & W ardougne, falador, yanille... [/li] [li]many things added like attaching shards for a godsword: but I don't know if i will include gs ingame since it's a real oldschool[/li] [li]old rsps slayer: proceed the floors in the slayer tower -no tasks[/li] [li]npc thieving supported + stalls with the right items[/li] [li]agility gnome course with yelling gnome and ticket exchange [/li] [li]Perfecting skills - many thanks to Imsuperman05!, example: all trees are available like teak and mahogany[/li] [li]hidden futures ingame and unique possibilities with the quest skill [/li] [li]awesome rs beginner tutorial (video included under text)[/li] [li]custom merchant system, not perfected yet[/li] [li]magebook sprites edited, e.g. edgville teleport actually shows an E [/li][/list][img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/3934/edg.png[/img]
[size=13pt][b]Beginners tutorial video:[/b][/size] [img]http://img249.imageshack.us/img249/4723/youtubeiconna.png[/img] Currently completing the video, gets uploaded soon
[size=13pt]Media: [/size] [size=8pt][i]I didn't know a good website with slide-show, and I have to much media to just post it here so did it on an fb page, if u know a good one please tell me.[/i][/size] [url=http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=234137759975659&set=pu.234134203309348&type=1&theater]http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=234137759975659&set=pu.234134203309348&type=1&theater[/url] or if not working: [url=http://www.facebook.com/pages/Fantasy-World/234134203309348]http://www.facebook.com/pages/Fantasy-World/234134203309348[/url]
